elaka]]<br/>'''Seasonal:''' [[Hat Yai International Airport|Hat Yai]]\n| [[Qatar Airways]] | [[Hamad International Airport|Doha]]\n| [[Qingdao Airlines]] | [[Quanzhou Jinjiang International Airport|Quanzhou]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Qingdao Airlines plans new international routes in 4Q19 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/286883/qingdao-airlines-plans-new-international-routes-in-4q19/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=15 October 2019}}</ref>\n| [[Scoot]] | [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]\n| [[Shenzhen Airlines]] | [[Shenzhen Bao'an International Airport|Shenzhen]]<ref>https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/287372/shenzhen-airlines-schedules-new-international-routes-from-shenzhen-in-dec-2019/</ref>\n| [[SilkAir]] | [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]\n| [[Sriwijaya Air]] | [[Kuala Namu International Airport|Medan]]\n| [[Starlux Airlines]] | [[Taoyuan International Airport|Taipei\u2013Taoyuan]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onemileatatime.com/starlux-airlines/|title=Starlux Airlines: Taiwan's AWESOME New Airline|date=7 October 2019|website=One Mile at a Time}}</ref>\n| [[Thai AirAsia]] | [[Don Mueang International Airport|Bangkok\u2013Don Mueang]]\n| [[Thai Smile]] | [[Suvarnabhumi Airport|Bangkok\u2013Suvarnabhumi]] \n}}\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport destination list\n|[[Cathay Pacific Cargo]]|[[Soekarno Hatta International Airport|Jakarta\u2013Soekarno\u2013Hatta]], [[Tan Son Nhat International Airport|Ho Chi Minh City]], [[Hong Kong International Airport|Hong Kong]], [[Phnom Penh International Airport|Phnom Penh]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/245315/cathay-pacific-cargo-adds-phnom-penh-service-from-late-nov-2014/|title=Cathay Pacific Cargo Adds Phnom Penh Service from late-Nov 2014|publisher=Routes Online|date=6 November 2014|accessdate=23 September 2017}}</ref> [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]\n|[[China Airlines Cargo]]|[[Noi Bai International Airport|Hanoi]], [[Ta