d at least 120 described species in Calamoceratidae.<ref name=bugref>{{Cite web| title=Calamoceratidae Family Information| url=https://bugguide.net/node/view/302843| website=BugGuide.net| accessdate=2018-02-23}}</ref><ref name=itis>{{Cite web| title=Calamoceratidae Report| url=https://www.itis.gov/servlet/SingleRpt/SingleRpt?search_topic=TSN&search_value=116529| website=Integrated Taxonomic Information System| accessdate=2018-02-23}}</ref><ref name=eol>{{Cite web| title=Calamoceratidae Overview| url=http://eol.org/pages/1112/overview| website=Encyclopedia of Life| accessdate=2018-02-23}}</ref><ref name=catlife>{{Cite web| title=Browse Calamoceratidae| url=http://www.catalogueoflife.org/col/browse/tree/id/043db06b3f0d289c0a01273327a31aba| website=Catalogue of Life| accessdate=2018-02-23}}</ref>\n\nITIS [[Taxonomy|Taxonomic]] note: <!-- This is a public domain ITIS comment -->\n*Type genus: Calamoceras F Brauer, 1865.<ref name=itis/>\n\n==Genera==\n* ''[[Anisocentropus]]'' <small>McLachlan, 1863</small>\n* ''[[Ascalaphomerus]]'' <small>Walker, 1852</small>\n* ''[[Banyallarga]]'' <small>Navas, 1916</small>\n* ''[[Calamoceras]]'' <small>Brauer, 1865</small>\n* ''[[Ganonema]]'' <small>McLachlan, 1866</small>\n* ''[[Georgium (caddisfly)|Georgium]]'' <small>Fischer, 1964</small>\n* ''[[Heteroplectron]]'' <small>McLachlan, 1871</small>\n* ''[[Phylloicus]]'' <small>Mueller, 1880</small>\n* ''[[Silvatares]]'' <small>Nav\u00e1s, 1931</small>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last1 = Kellogg | first1 = Vernon L.\n| date = 1905\n| title = American insects\n| publisher = H. Holt\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last1 = Arnett | first1 = Ross H. Jr.\n| date = 2000\n| title = American Insects: A Handbook of the Insects of America North of Mexico\n| publisher = CRC Press\n| volume = 2nd Edition\n| isbn = 0-8493-0212-9\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n| last1 = Merritt \n| last2 = Cummins \n| last3 = Berg \n| date = 2008\n| title = Aquatic Insects of North