hter and merry singing sessions, the housemates get their first task, which leaves everyone teary-eyed.<ref>{{cite news|title=Somadas dedicates a song for his little daughter|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-somadas-dedicates-a-song-for-his-little-daughter/articleshow/73157132.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 4\n| Rajith's Tale and the First Argument in House\n| {{Start date|2020|01|08}}\n| As the housemates take turns to share their life stories, Rajithkumar's tale leaves everyone shell-shocked.<ref>{{cite news|title=Rajith's life story triggers the first argument in the house|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-update-day-3-rajiths-life-story-triggers-the-first-argument-in-the-house/articleshow/73166450.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5\n| Day 4 in the House\n| {{Start date|2020|01|09}}\n| The wave of emotions continues to sweep over the house even today. While Somadas' story touches hearts, Shaji gets into limelight for his style of expression.\n|-\n| 6\n| Arya's Heartbreaking Story\n| {{Start date|2020|01|10}}\n| The housemates have gala time as they play a fun game. Later, Arya, the girl who makes everyone laugh shares the heart-breaking story of her life.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sujo confesses his love for Alasandra|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-preview-january-10-sujo-confesses-his-love-for-alasandra/articleshow/73189747.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|7\n| Dharmajan's Unexpected Entry & Exit\n| {{Start date|2020|01|11}}\n| To everyone\u2019s surprise, Dharmajan Bolgatty, a comic actor enters the house initially disguised as an emtrant and spends a night with the contestants with fun-filled talks. However, it was short-lived as Mohanlal asks him to come out leaving everyone else confused and sad. \n|- \n| 8 \n| The New Captain is Shaji \n| {{Start date|2020|01|12}}\n| To elect a new captain, Mohanlal giv