housemates of targeting him and Pavan\n| {{Start date|2020|02|12}}\n| As the housemates get back from their health check-up, Pavan creates a ruckus as his luxury budget coins go missing. The house is on fire as everyone fights and steals for their points.\n|-\n| 40\n| Fukru and Rajith to end up in a scuffle\n| {{Start date|2020|02|13}}\n| What started as a fun game, brings Fukru and Rajith at loggerheads. If that wasn't enough, BB threw in a new twist leaving the housemates stupefied.\n|-\n| 41\n| Pavan Thomas leaves the house due to a medical emergency\n| {{Start date|2020|02|14}}\n| Apart from infections and allergies, love is also in the air today. As the housemates indulge in Valentine's special activities, a shock awaits them.\n|-\n| 42\n| Mohanlal questions housemates about the ruckus in the house\n| {{Start date|2020|02|15}}\n| With Mohanlal in the house, it's time for some grilling. From discussing the fights to the captaincy task, he has a lot to talk about.\n|-\n| 43\n| Pradeep Chandran gets evicted\n| {{Start date|2020|02|16}}\n| When messages from families make the housemates emotional, Mohanlal peps up the mood with an exciting game. He also has the verdict for the day.<ref>{{cite news|title=Pradeep Chandran gets evicted|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-update-february-16-pradeep-chandran-gets-evicted/articleshow/74169246.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 44\n| Fukru and Rajith lock horns during the task\n| {{Start date|2020|02|17}}\n| As the housemates vote for this week's nomination, a new name comes up in the list.\n|-\n| 45\n| Contestants to face yet another nomination\n| {{Start date|2020|02|18}}\n| Superheroes and supervillains in the house today! The luxury budget task leaves the housemates in splits.\n|-\n| 46\n| Fukru accuses Rajith of choking him with a shawl; calls him a 'beast' while Fukru kicks Rajith on the chest\n| {{Start date|2020|02|19}}\n| As the task continues and competition gets tough, housemates make new strategies to win.\n|-\n| 47\n| Rajith and Fukru get jailed\n| {{Start date|2020|02|20}}\n| The housemates have to take decisions - not one, but two.\n|}\n\n====BB Cafe====\n''BB Cafe'' is an [[aftershow]] hosted by Rajesh Keshav and Gopika that discusses episodes aired on the previous day. Each episode is approximately five minutes long. ''BB Cafe Live'', a 30-minute live show is also aired daily on Asianet's [[YouTube]] channel that discuss the live comments on YouTube.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\n|-\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| {{abbr|Ep. No.|Episode Number}}\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Title\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Original airing\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Short summary\n|-\n|1\n|The Cafe Opens\n|6 January 2020\n|Chat session with Rajesh and Gopika discuss the premiere episode.\n|-\n|2\n|All About Arya and Fukru\n|7 January 2020\n|Rajesh and Gopika discuss Fukru's love story and Arya's cooking session in the Bigg Boss.\n|-\n|3\n|Gopika is Impressed\n|8 January 2020\n|Gopika is impressed with RJ Raghu's story. Rajesh has a personal favourite in the house.\n|-\n|4\n|Rajesh Adores Somu\n|9 January 2020\n|While Rajesh shares about Somu's musical skills, Gopika has some soft corner for Veena and Arya.\n|-\n|5\n|Rajith Faces the Jury\n|10 January 2020\n|Rajesh and Gopika talk about Rajith's behaviour with the other contestants. They also discuss Somu's story.\n|-\n|6\n|All About the Surprise\n|11 January 2020\n|Gopika and Rajesh share their excitement about Mohanlal's entry in the house and the surprise visit of a stranger.\n|-\n|7\n|Hot Gossip\n|12 January 2020\n|Rajesh and Gopika get together to talk about the latest and hottest news from the Bigg Boss house.\n|-\n|8\n|Crucial Moments to Come\n|13 January 2020\n|Rajesh and Gopika discuss Mohanlal's visit to the house. They also talk about the upcoming evictions.\n|-\n