 scope=\"col\" | [[Season premiere]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[Season finale]]\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#DEAA88; color:#100;\" |\n| [[Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 1)|1]]\n| 99\n| {{Start date|df=yes|2018|06|24}}\n| {{Start date|df=yes|2018|09|30}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#100;\" |\n| [[Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 2)|2]]\n| {{Age in days|2020|1|5}}\n| {{Start date|df=yes|2020|1|5}}\n| {{TBA}}\n|}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Episodes==\n=== Season 1 (2018) ===\n{{main|Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 1)}}\nThe first season premiered on 24 June 2018 and ended on 30 September 2018. The house was built at [[Mumbai]] where 18 housemates contested (two of them being wildcard entries). [[Mohanlal]] was the host of the season. [[Sabumon Abdusamad]] emerged as the winner after 98 days.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"6\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#DEAA88; color:#FFFFFF;| {{abbr|Ep. No.|Episode Number}}\n! style=\"background:#DEAA88; color:#FFFFFF;| Title\n! style=\"background:#DEAA88; color:#FFFFFF;| Original airing\n! style=\"background:#DEAA88; color:#FFFFFF;| Short summary\n|-\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>Mohanlal's roaring reality show</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|24}}\n| 16 contestants, 100 days of unlimited drama, all in one 'Bigg' house. Catch Mollywood's complete actor, Mohanlal light the fuse to the biggest live reality show in Malayalam.<ref>{{cite news|title=Mohanlal locks the 16 contestants with a 'Manichithra Poottu'|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-24-2018-mohanlal-locks-the-16-contestants-with-a-manichithra-poottu/articleshow/64733297.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>2</center>\n| <center>Aditi Rai gets maximum nominations for eviction</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|25}}\n| Less than a day's stay in the Bigg Boss house, Aditi faces personal comments and ends up shattered in tears. The eventful day simmers down with the first captain being selected.<ref>{{cite news|title=Aditi Rai gets maximum nominations for eviction|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-25-2018-aditi-rai-gets-maximum-nominations-for-eviction/articleshow/64745083.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>3</center>\n| <center>Diya and Aditi get into an argument</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|26}}\n| The housemates face their first ever luxury budget task which requires them to dance as ordered.<ref>{{cite news|title=Diya and Aditi get into an argument\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-26-2018-diya-and-aditi-get-into-an-argument/articleshow/64763383.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>4</center>\n| <center>Manoj collapses</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|27}}\n| The luxury budget task continues as the housemates are divided into two teams, Mohanlal and Mammootty. Manoj collapses after the task and is rushed to the hospital for treatment.<ref>{{cite news|title=Contestants dress up as Mammootty and Mohanlal\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-27-2018-contestants-dress-up-as-mammootty-and-mohanlal/articleshow/64776246.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>5</center>\n| <center>Manoj Verma makes his exit from Bigg Boss house</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|28}}\n| Catch the reaction of the housemates as tension builds between Sreenish and Archana. Witness an unexpected departure as a contestant is asked to leave the house.<ref>{{cite news|title=Manoj Varma makes his exit from the Bigg Boss house\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-28-2018-manoj-varma-makes-his-exit-from-the-bigg-boss-house/articleshow/64791218.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>6</center>\n| <center>Underwear is a Luxury!</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|29}}\n| Bigg Boss uses the luxury budget as a unique way of addressing Suresh's request for extra underwears. Catch the reaction of the housemates as they get their first luxury supplies.<ref>{{cite news|title=Housemates divide themselves into groups\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-june-29-2018-housemates-divide-themselves-into-groups/articleshow/64804453.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>7</center>\n| <center>Mixed Bag of Emotions</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|06|30}}\n| Mohanlal is back and this time he comes bearing gifts and happy news. Ranjini's captaincy is off to a rough start as the housemates turn against her. Catch the Superstar as he builds up the tension for the first round of eliminations.<ref>{{cite news|title=David John and Aditi Rai to be eliminated?\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-june-30-2018-david-john-and-aditi-rai-to-be-eliminated/articleshow/64814348.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>8</center>\n| <center>May the Famous be saved</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|07|01}}\n| Mohanlal takes the eviction to the next level with a unique popularity poll task. Find out who will be voted as the least popular contestant, paving his or her way to an early exit from the house.<ref>{{cite news|title=David John gets evicted\n|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-written-update-july-1-2018-david-john-gets-evicted/articleshow/64824199.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>9</center>\n| <center>Playing a double game</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|07|02}}\n| Pearle and Sreelakshmi face severe criticism for their two-faced gameplay. With the next elimination around the corner, will these accusations lead them to being nominated?\n|-\n| <center>10</center>\n| <center>Luxury Task Turns Rough</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|07|03}}\n| The luxury budget task, designed to test the business abilities of the housemates, brings out the violent side in some. Amid