 Surprise</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|09|29}}\n| Bigg Boss gives a grand surprise to the housemates leaving them awestruck.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bigg Boss house welcomes the former contestants|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-day-97-live-update-ex-contestants-to-make-a-surprise-visit/liveblog/66009196.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>99</center>\n| <center>The Grand Finale Is Here</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|09|30}}\n| The finale promises flashy lights, rocking performances and loads of entertainment. There is excitement in the air as Mohanlal discloses the name of the winner.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sabumon is the winner of Mohanlal\u2019s show|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/television/bigg-boss-malayalam-finale-live-updates-5380336/|work=indianexpress.com}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Season 2 (2020) ===\n{{main|Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 2)}}\nThe second season premiered on 5 January 2019. [[Mohanlal]] returned as the host. The house was built at [[Chennai]], where 17 contestants entered on day-1.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\n|-\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| {{abbr|Ep. No.|Episode Number}}\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Title\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Original airing\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Short summary\n|-\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>The Grand Launch</center>\n| {{Start date|2020|01|05}}\n| The brand new season of ''Bigg Boss'' is here! Superstar Mohanlal welcomes seventeen new housemates, who are eager to begin their journey in the Bigg Boss ouse. Watch the legend get the ball rolling, however, with a twist in the tale.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bigg Boss Malayalam Season 2 Launch Highlights: The grand reality show witnessed the entry of 17 contestants|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-launch-live-updates-the-reality-show-is-all-set-to-start/liveblog/73108581.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2\n| First Captain \n| {{Start date|2020|01|06}}\n| As the housemates try to know each other and acquaint themselves with their new abode, Bigg Boss throws open the first challenge. It's time to choose the captain and it won't be easy.\n|-\n| 3\n| The Yearn for their Families\n| {{Start date|2020|01|07}}\n| Amidst all the fun, laughter and merry singing sessions, the housemates get their first task, which leaves everyone teary-eyed.<ref>{{cite news|title=Somadas dedicates a song for his little daughter|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-somadas-dedicates-a-song-for-his-little-daughter/articleshow/73157132.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 4\n| Rajith's Tale and the First Argument in House\n| {{Start date|2020|01|08}}\n| As the housemates take turns to share their life stories, Rajithkumar's tale leaves everyone shell-shocked.<ref>{{cite news|title=Rajith's life story triggers the first argument in the house|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-update-day-3-rajiths-life-story-triggers-the-first-argument-in-the-house/articleshow/73166450.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5\n| Day 4 in the House\n| {{Start date|2020|01|09}}\n| The wave of emotions continues to sweep over the house even today. While Somadas' story touches hearts, Shaji gets into limelight for his style of expression.\n|-\n| 6\n| Arya's Heartbreaking Story\n| {{Start date|2020|01|10}}\n| The housemates have gala time as they play a fun game. Later, Arya, the girl who makes everyone laugh shares the heart-breaking story of her life.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sujo confesses his love for Alasandra|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-preview-january-10-sujo-confesses-his-love-for-alasandra/articleshow/73189747.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|7\n| Dharmajan's Unexpected Entry & Exit\n| {{Start date|2020|01|11}}\n|